69151dbe-bda7-4527-98ac-97ed4d5468cc.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
69151dbe-bda7-4527-98ac-97ed4d5468cc.text: Don't mind me parrot, he's Cracked Jenny's Tea Cup!

options.text: What do I do in the arena?
I'd like to use the Agility Arena, please.
Can you tell me a bit about the Skillcape of Agility, please?

4b9a6e88-6c87-4742-b8c1-074120577249.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
4b9a6e88-6c87-4742-b8c1-074120577249.text:
This, me hearty, is the entrance to the Brimhaven
Agility Arena!

9b38474c-dd1c-4ce7-add9-a759849c34a2.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
9b38474c-dd1c-4ce7-add9-a759849c34a2.text:
I were diggin for buried treasure when I found it!
Amazed I was! It was a sight to behold!

68b21058-596d-4656-97e6-6ca034aef5c4.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
68b21058-596d-4656-97e6-6ca034aef5c4.text:
It were the biggest thing I'd ever seen! It must've been
at least a league from side to side!

e2231a28-3d67-46cc-97d9-cc7d7ddb0e0f.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
e2231a28-3d67-46cc-97d9-cc7d7ddb0e0f.text: It made me list, I were that excited!

53505a15-45cd-46d1-90a9-bbad89559f6c.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
53505a15-45cd-46d1-90a9-bbad89559f6c.text:
I'd found a huge cave with all these platforms. I reckon
it be an ancient civilisation that made it. I had to be
mighty careful as there was these traps everywhere!
Dangerous it was!

9fd1b14d-2a8e-436f-8b01-f0f5bc9c278b.title: <player>
9fd1b14d-2a8e-436f-8b01-f0f5bc9c278b.text: What do I do in the arena?

60e8ae9a-c12d-4fe8-ae9c-c96d600136c2.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
60e8ae9a-c12d-4fe8-ae9c-c96d600136c2.text:
Well, me hearty, it's simple. Ye can cross between two
platforms by using the traps or obstacles strung across
'em. Try and make your way to the pillar that is
indicated by the flashing arrow.

47d23b3c-7c7b-4fc7-9b22-bb0411b9c675.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
47d23b3c-7c7b-4fc7-9b22-bb0411b9c675.text:
Ye receive tickets for tagging more than one pillar in a
row. So ye won't get a ticket from the first pillar but
ye will for every platform ye tag in a row after that.

1ebed755-0851-429d-85df-eb3b954a727e.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
1ebed755-0851-429d-85df-eb3b954a727e.text:
If ye miss a platform ye will miss out on the next ticket
so try and get every platform you can! When ye be
done, take the tickets to Jackie over there and she'll
exchange them for more stuff!

b9227d9c-fb82-4d52-9670-b052923b70e4.title: Parrot
b9227d9c-fb82-4d52-9670-b052923b70e4.text:
Tag when green light means tickets!
Tag when red light means green light!

69d9bce1-91af-4cbc-b1a3-8c113caa9065.title: <player>
69d9bce1-91af-4cbc-b1a3-8c113caa9065.text: I'd like to use the Agility Arena, please.

525093aa-da67-419f-a4a1-fc4f9cdb3bae.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
525093aa-da67-419f-a4a1-fc4f9cdb3bae.text:
A word of warning me hearty! There are dangerous
traps down there!

b1a094ab-535f-4e8b-9c2b-21449d40509c.title: Postpone
b1a094ab-535f-4e8b-9c2b-21449d40509c.text: Missing take coins & enter, awaiting Brimhaven agility arena

a31764f9-c42a-43fd-9d80-a2994e90dd0a.title: <player>
a31764f9-c42a-43fd-9d80-a2994e90dd0a.text:
Can you tell me a bit about the Skillcape of Agility,
please?

b83b42ca-9afe-4434-8e2b-023e0d705181.title: Cap'n Izzy No-Beard
b83b42ca-9afe-4434-8e2b-023e0d705181.text:
Aye, to be sure! The Skillcape of Agility be the symbol
of the master of dexterity! Providing weight reduction,
one who wears it can climb like a cat, run like the wind
and jump like...err, well, jump like a jumping thing!
